<concept id="id" class="- topic/topic concept/concept "><title class="- topic/title ">Link test runs to Jira defects in <ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-testops" class="- topic/ph "/></title><conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody "><p class="- topic/p ">If a Test Run fails, you can link its Test Result to Jira issues, such as Jira Bugs. You can then view the Test Result of that Test Run in Jira to investigate the Defects.</p><note type="important" class="- topic/note "><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">You have installed the <xref format="html" href="https://marketplace.atlassian.com/apps/1217501/katalon-bdd-test-automation-for-jira" scope="external" class="- topic/xref ">Jira App</xref>.</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">You have configured Jira integration. See: <xref href="../../../../Organize/Integration_For_Organizing_Tests/Jira_Integration/Enable-Jira-TestOps-integration/intro-jira-configuration-in-TestOps.dita" class="- topic/xref ">Jira Settings</xref>.</p></li></ul></note><section class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Requirements</title><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">In Jira, install this plugin from the Atlassian Marketplace website: <xref format="html" href="https://marketplace.atlassian.com/apps/1217501/katalon-bdd-test-automation-for-jira" scope="external" class="- topic/xref ">Katalon Studio and TestOps integration.</xref></p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">You have configured Jira integration. See: <xref href="../../../../Organize/Integration_For_Organizing_Tests/Jira_Integration/Enable-Jira-TestOps-integration/intro-jira-configuration-in-TestOps.dita" class="- topic/xref "/>.</p></li></ul></section></conbody></concept>